* Season 5 began airing on ETV2 in September 2010.

a
* The show will begin airing on 22 February 2012 on Studio B. All six seasons will be shown.

o
* The TV audience in Montenegro also can watch Outrageous Fortune (Strijele sudbine) on state television TV CG 1. The last season will air at the end of April 2012.

